title: Ubon Ratchathani University Stadium
text: Ubon Ratchathani University Stadium () is a <a href="multi-purpose%20stadium">multi-purpose stadium</a> in <a href="Ubon%20Ratchathani%20Province">Ubon Ratchathani Province</a> , <a href="Thailand">Thailand</a>. It is currently used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and is the home stadium of <a href="Ubon%20Ratchathani%20F.C.">Ubon Ratchathani F.C.</a>.
